headline: TASTE OF THE NFL BRINGS SUPER BOWL LX'S ULTIMATE CULINARY EXPERIENCE TO SAN FRANCISCO TO RALLY SUPPORT TO END STUDENT HUNGER
summary: Get ready for an unforgettable culinary and gridiron adventure that scores big for students in need! Taste of the NFL returns to the Bay Area with an extraordinary fusion of world-class cuisine, gridiron greats, and purposeful giving – all dedicated to GENYOUth's critical work to help end student hunger and foster nutrition security nationwide.

content.title: TASTE OF THE NFL BRINGS SUPER BOWL LX'S ULTIMATE CULINARY EXPERIENCE TO SAN FRANCISCO TO RALLY SUPPORT TO END STUDENT HUNGER
content.summary: Get ready for an unforgettable culinary and gridiron adventure that scores big for students in need! Taste of the NFL returns to the Bay Area with an extraordinary fusion of world-class cuisine, gridiron greats, and purposeful giving – all dedicated to GENYOUth's critical work to help end student hunger and foster nutrition security nationwide.

thumbnail.caption: Taste of the NFL returns to the Bay Area with an extraordinary fusion of world class chefs, incredible cuisine, gridiron greats, extraordinary entertainment, and purposeful giving to benefit national nonprofit GENYOUth's mission to help end student hunger and foster nutrition security. Presented by PepsiCo, Super Bowl LX’s largest philanthropic event will take place February 7, 2026, from 4 p.m. to 7 p.m. PST at The Hibernia in San Francisco.

headline: Assessing PepsiCo (PEP) Valuation After CES 2026 AI Partnership With Siemens And NVIDIA
summary: At CES 2026, PepsiCo (PEP) outlined a multi-year collaboration with Siemens and NVIDIA to use digital twin technology and AI across its plants and warehouses, putting operational efficiency and capital discipline in sharper investor focus.
